        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553a10_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當作是學。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553a10_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時，諸比丘聞佛所說，歡喜奉行。",
