        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，諸比丘聞佛所說，歡喜奉行。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b05_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "（八）聞如是：一時，佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊告諸比丘：「當修行一法，當廣布一法；便成神通，除諸亂想，獲沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何為一法？",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂念安般。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b10_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當善修行，當廣演布，便成神通，去諸亂想，獲沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b12_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當修行一法，當廣布一法。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b12_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b13_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當作是學。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b13_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，諸比丘聞佛所說，歡喜奉行。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b13_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "（九）聞如是：一時，佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊告諸比丘：「當修行一法，當廣布一法；便成神通，除諸亂想，逮沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何為一法？",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂念身非常。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當善修行，當廣演布，便成神通，去眾亂想，得沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b18_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當修行一法，當廣布一法。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b21_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當作是學。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b21_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，諸比丘聞佛所說，歡喜奉行。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b21_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "（一〇）聞如是：一時，佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊告諸比丘：「當修行一法，當廣布一法；便成神通，除諸亂想，獲沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何為一法？",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂念死。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當善修行，當廣演布，便成神通，去眾亂想，得沙門果，自致涅槃。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b26_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b28_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當修行一法，當廣布一法。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b28_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，諸比丘！",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b29_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當作是學。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b29_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，諸比丘聞佛所說，歡喜奉行。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553b29_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　佛、法、聖眾念　　戒、施及天念　休息、安般念　　身、死念在後增壹阿含經卷第一「『「於今我首上，　　已生衰耗毛；　　　天使已來至，　　宜當時出家。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553c02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『「我今已食人中之福，宜當自勉昇天之德，剃除鬚髮，著三法衣，以信堅固，出家學道，離於眾苦。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553c07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『時，長壽王告第一太子善觀曰：「卿今知不？",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553c09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "吾已首上生白髮，意欲剃除鬚髮，著三法衣，以信堅固，出家學道，離於眾苦。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553c10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝紹吾位，以法治化，勿令有失，違吾言教，造凡夫行。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553c12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以然者，若有斯人，違吾言者，為凡夫之行。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553c13_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夫凡夫者，長處三塗、八難之中。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553c14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時，王長壽八萬四千歲善修梵行，行四等心，慈、悲、喜、護，身逝命終，生梵天上。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553c15_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時，王善觀憶父王教，未曾暫捨，以法治化，無有阿曲。』",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553c16_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「迦葉！",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553c18_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "知不？",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553c18_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時摩訶提婆，豈異人乎？",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553c18_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "莫作是觀，爾時王者，今釋迦文是；時長壽王者，今阿難身是；爾時善觀者，今優多羅比丘是；恒受王法未曾捨忘，亦不斷絕。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553c19_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時，善觀王復興父王勅，以法治化，不斷王教。",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553c22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以然者，以父王教，難得違故。」",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553c23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，尊者阿難便說偈曰：",
        "from": "T02n0125_001:0553c23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]